sofmerril.org/sol20b.html#Jon%20Lomberg">"Tribute"</a>. <i>SOL Rising, Number 20, January 1998</i>. The Friends of the <a href="/wiki/Judith_Merril" title="Judith Merril">Judith Merril</a> Collection, <a href="/wiki/Toronto_Public_Library" title="Toronto Public Library">Toronto Public Library</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJon+Lomberg&amp;rft.atitle=Tribute&amp;rft.au=Jon+Lomberg&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=SOL+Rising%2C+Number+20%2C+January+1998&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.friendsofmerril.org%2Fsol20b.html%23Jon%2520Lomberg&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-CBCMcDonaldVoyager-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-CBCMcDonaldVoyager_6-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news"><a href="/wiki/Bob_McDonald_(science_journalist)" title="Bob McDonald (science journalist)">Bob McDonald</a> (September 6, 2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cbc.ca/technology/quirks-blog/2007/09/30_years_and_a_day.html">"30 Years and a Day"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Quirks_and_Quarks" class="mw-redirect" title="Quirks and Quarks">Quirks and Quarks</a></i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJon+Lomberg&amp;rft.atitle=30+Years+and+a+Day&amp;rft.au=Bob+McDonald&amp;rft.date=2007-09-06&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Quirks+and+Quarks&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Ftechnology%2Fquirks-blog%2F2007%2F09%2F30_years_and_a_day.html&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-CBCVirtualViking-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-CBCVirtualViking_7-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href=